<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.8.7">
<l>tēṉuka ṉāvi pōyuka vaṅkōr ceḻuntiraḷ paṉaṅkaṉi yutira</l>
<l>tāṉukan teṟinta taṭaṅkaṭal vaṇṇa reṇṇimu ṉiṭaṅkoṇṭa kōyil</l>
<l>vāṉakac cōlai marakatac cāyal māmaṇik kallatar niṟaintu</l>
<l>māṉukar cāral māliruñ cōlai vaṇaṅkutum vāmaṭa neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Come, simple heart, we will worship in Māliruñcōlai</l>
<l rend="indent">where deer graze on slopes,</l>
<l>Abounding along paths of dark gemstones in the emerald shade</l>
<l rend="indent">of a sky-high forest,</l>
<l>The temple where the one of the wide sea’s hue, choosing [it],</l>
<l rend="indent">previously took his place,</l>
<l>Who happily threw Dhenuka, so his life spilled out and was gone,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] so a fat, round palm fruit fell there.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
